@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 说明
# 1. 先运行 00-seed-data.http
# 2. 这个文件专门测试首页聚合接口和首页搜索接口
# 3. 重点观察：
#    - baseQuarterOverview：只受 year + quarter + category 影响
#    - viewQuarterOverview：受 category + status + keyword 等当前筛选影响

### =========================
### quarter-dashboard 测试
### =========================

### 1. 默认 ANIME，观察 base / view 概览是否一致
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=1

### 2. ANIME + WATCHED，观察 base 不变、view 缩小
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&status=WATCHED

### 3. ANIME + keyword=巨人，观察 base 不变、view 缩小
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&keyword=巨人

### 4. ANIME + WATCHED + keyword=巨人，观察 view 进一步缩小
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&status=WATCHED&keyword=巨人

### 5. COMIC 侧首页，观察 base / view
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=2&category=COMIC

### 6. COMIC + ON_HOLD
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=2&category=COMIC&status=ON_HOLD

### 7. ANIME + 评分降序
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/quarter-dashboard?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&recordSort=SCORE_DESC

### =========================
### search 测试
### =========================

### 8. 默认全作品库搜索（LIBRARY）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/search?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&keyword=巨人

### 9. 已记录库搜索（RECORDED）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/search?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&keyword=巨人&scope=RECORDED

### 10. 漫画作品库搜索
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/search?year=2024&quarter=2&category=COMIC&keyword=蓝色&scope=LIBRARY

### 11. 漫画已记录库搜索
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/search?year=2024&quarter=2&category=COMIC&keyword=蓝色&scope=RECORDED

### 12. 非法搜索：关键词为空
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/home/search?year=2024&quarter=1&category=ANIME&keyword=